 style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3785803" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/taylor-swift@2000x1270-3.jpg" alt="泰勒·斯威夫特 (Taylor Swift) 8 月 15 日在温布利球场表演" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/taylor-swift@2000x1270-3.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/taylor-swift@2000x1270-3-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/taylor-swift@2000x1270-3-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/taylor-swift@2000x1270-3-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/taylor-swift@2000x1270-3-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/taylor-swift@2000x1270-3-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3785803" class="wp-caption-text">泰勒·斯威夫特。图片来源：凯特·格林/盖蒂图片社</figcaption></figure><p>斯威夫特和埃米纳姆都角逐当晚最负盛名的奖项——年度最佳视频奖。四届得奖者斯威夫特<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/here-are-all-the-winners-from-the-2023-mtv-vmas-3496804">凭借《反英雄》成为目前的获奖者</a>，而埃米纳姆多年来已创纪录地获得了该奖项的七次提名。获得该奖项的还有 Grande、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/billie-eilish">Billie Eilish</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/doja-cat">Doja Cat</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sza">SZA</a> 。</p><p>与此同时，年度艺术家奖由斯威夫特、阿姆、格兰德、SZA、卡彭特和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/bad-bunny">坏兔子</a>获得，而年度歌曲则由斯威夫特、卡彭特、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/beyonce">碧昂丝</a>、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jack-harlow">杰克·哈洛</a>、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/kendrick-lamar">肯德里克·拉马尔</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/teddy-swims">泰迪·斯威姆斯</a>获得。</p><p>韩国流行音乐组合<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/blackpink">BLACKPINK</a>的<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/olivia-rodrigo">奥利维亚·罗德里戈 (Olivia Rodrigo)</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/lisa">丽莎 (Lisa</a> ) 与 Swims 一样获得了四项提名，而布恩 (Boone)、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/dua-lipa">杜阿·利帕 (Dua Lipa)</a> 、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/anitta">安妮塔 (Anitta</a> )、泰拉 (Tyla)、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/bleachers">Bleachers</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/glorilla">GloRilla</a>都获得了三项提名。 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/cardi-b">Cardi B</a> &amp; <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/shakira">Shakira</a>和 Rauw Alejandro 等人与 Anitta 和 Bad Bunny 一起获得最佳拉丁音乐奖，而<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/megan-thee-stallion">Megan Thee Stallion</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/travis-scott">Travis Scott 则</a>跻身最佳嘻哈音乐提名者之列。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/bon-jovi">Bon Jovi</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/coldplay">Coldplay</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/green-day">Green Day</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/lenny-kravitz">Lenny Kravitz</a>均获得最佳摇滚提名，而 Hozier 和 Linkin Park 则获得最佳另类音乐提名。</p><p>此外， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/katy-perry-to-receive-video-vanguard-award-at-the-mtv-vmas-3784261">凯蒂·佩里 (Katy Perry) 将获得视频先锋奖</a>，加入包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/missy-elliott">米西·埃利奥特 (Missy Elliott)</a> 、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/rihanna">蕾哈娜 (Rihanna</a> )、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/beyonce">碧昂丝 (Beyoncé)</a>和去年的获奖者<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/shakira">夏奇拉 (Shakira)</a>在内的著名获奖者阵容。时隔七年，佩里还将重返 VMA 舞台，演唱一系列她最热门的歌曲来庆祝该奖项。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/halsey-and-lenny-kravitz-to-perform-at-2024-vmas-3785912">哈尔西 (Halsey) 和伦尼·克拉维茨 (Lenny Kravitz) 在 2024 年 VMA 上表演的</a>消息首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
